ActCoasting Trade Act
SubjectRegulations Specifying Territories and Indicating International Registers
PrecisREGULATIONS SPECIFYING TERRITORIES AND INDICATING INTERNATIONAL REGISTERS in order to specify those territories not referred to in the definition of “territory of the European Union” and to indicate those registers that are international registers, for the purposes of applying the Coasting Trade Act.
